snippet: A Russian Soyuz capsule landed in the steppes of Kazakhstan, bringing home an American and two Russian astronauts from the International Space Station.
abstract: Russian Soyuz capsule lands in steppes of Kazakhstan, bringing home American and two Russian astronauts from International Space Station a day after their original return was delayed by foul weather.
lead_paragraph: A Russian Soyuz capsule landed in the steppes of Kazakhstan, bringing home an American and two Russian astronauts from the International Space Station.

headline.main: Kazakhstan: Space Station Crew Returns After a Daylong Delay
headline.print_headline: Kazakhstan: Space Station Crew Returns After a Daylong Delay
